00:10:05.065 --> 00:10:06.763
iz dos hobn zey arayn

00:10:07.900 --> 00:10:10.779
geyen, hobn mir a trunk geton befresye, un mir geyen aroys.

00:10:10.819 --> 00:10:13.243
zogn mir "mir geyn tsum sh- tsum shosey."

00:10:13.587 --> 00:10:17.293
hot m-, hot der yingl gezogt az itster az mir veln geyn tsum shosey

00:10:18.025 --> 00:10:19.689
ken men undz masern.

00:10:19.712 --> 00:10:21.755
⟨teytlen vos mir veln⟩ onkumen in shtetl

00:10:21.755 --> 00:10:24.175
efsher veyst men shoyn az di yidn, ver veys?

00:10:24.353 --> 00:10:27.573
kum, mir veln beser avekgeyn tifer in va- in, in dorf.

00:10:27.573 --> 00:10:30.390
hobn mir avek tifer in dorf un hot vayter azoy geton.

00:10:30.390 --> 00:10:33.441
hot er opgerukt dem shtang un mir arayngelozn

00:10:33.441 --> 00:10:36.471
un er hot zikh arayngekayklt durkhn fentster, durkh der efenung.

00:10:37.127 --> 00:10:40.310
un mir hobn ot azoy ibergeshlofn, un es iz shoyn montik.

00:10:40.519 --> 00:10:41.745
s'iz shoyn montik

00:10:41.953 --> 00:10:44.377
UNK mir dokh shabes aroysgelofn fun geto

00:10:44.535 --> 00:10:49.794
mir hobn shoyn oyfgegesn der shtik- do hobn mir nit gebetn keyn broyt. do in der khate hobn mir gebetn ⟨mer nit⟩ a trunk vaser.

00:10:49.918 --> 00:10:51.498
di broyt hobn mir oyfgegesn.

00:10:51.640 --> 00:10:54.266
azoy vi mir zitsn farbahaltn in di shtroy

00:10:54.458 --> 00:10:56.544
mir hern imitser iz arayn in shayer.

00:10:58.002 --> 00:10:59.582
arayn in shayer

00:10:59.773 --> 00:11:02.855
un er hot genumen zukhn a bintl UNK hot er undz gefunen.

00:11:03.047 --> 00:11:04.340
mir zaynen geven farbahaltn.

00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:07.024
zogn mir az ⟨m'iz⟩ mir zaynen yidn

00:11:07.198 --> 00:11:09.824
un efsher veyst ir avu iz do

00:11:10.303 --> 00:11:13.025
s- ELENA SKVRANYUK, avu iz ir khate?

00:11:13.025 --> 00:11:15.832
ikh dertseyl az zi iz geven bay undz di dinst

00:11:15.872 --> 00:11:19.173
un zi hot khasene gehat fun undz, mayn mame hot ir geholfn.

00:11:19.956 --> 00:11:22.700
geyt er arayn in shtub un dertseylt dos zayn vayb.

00:11:23.382 --> 00:11:26.042
iz zi gekumen, farbrokhn di hent

00:11:26.115 --> 00:11:27.656
un khapt mir kushn.

00:11:27.656 --> 00:11:29.518
zi fleg kumen tsu LENAn

00:11:29.693 --> 00:11:33.136
in Grodne koyfn a mantl, epes zakhn in der shtot

00:11:33.136 --> 00:11:35.466
flegt ir di mame zeyer gut oyfnemen

00:11:35.466 --> 00:11:38.034
gebn ir esn, gebn ir tey mit tsuker

00:11:38.034 --> 00:11:41.009
m- gebakte, iz bay undz dokh shtendik geven gebakte

00:11:41.117 --> 00:11:43.190
iz zi, iz, gedenkt zi dos

00:11:43.190 --> 00:11:49.971
un zi zogt. "TY SHE DOCH'KA BOGATIRA." du bist dokh a tokhter fun a raykher man. zi hot gekent mayne eltern.

00:11:51.276 --> 00:11:53.770
zi geyt epes opkokhn. gut, zitsn mir.

00:11:53.770 --> 00:11:55.910
er hot undz gezogt, der man, ven er iz nokh geven

00:11:55.910 --> 00:11:59.620
az mir darfn geyn glaykh, un di letste khate, dos iz LENA's, ⟨der⟩ dinst.

00:12:00.338 --> 00:12:03.437
iz arayn, un zi hot opgekokht a groysn top

00:12:03.477 --> 00:12:05.431
mit kartofl, a zup

00:12:05.431 --> 00:12:07.976
oy, UNK geton mit grinsn

00:12:08.100 --> 00:12:10.136
un farks- un mit

00:12:10.210 --> 00:12:13.126
farfetst mit di, s'iz mit khazer zikher

00:12:13.126 --> 00:12:14.371
mit di shmalts

00:12:14.462 --> 00:12:18.070
un broyt ongeshnitn efsher a, a kilo far mir un far im

00:12:18.070 --> 00:12:22.100
mit tsvey leflen. mir hobn dos oyfgegesn UNK nit gegleybt, a varemer esn

00:12:22.883 --> 00:12:26.685
un, hot zi gezogt "az ir vet iberlebn di milkhome zolt ir kumen tsu mir."

00:12:26.685 --> 00:12:27.669
hert zikh ayn.

00:12:28.924 --> 00:12:30.166
meyle

00:12:30.493 --> 00:12:32.102
az s'iz gevorn tunkl

00:12:32.102 --> 00:12:36.866
geyen mir tsu LENAn. az mir kumen tsu ir, hot zi oy- hot zi zikh ibergetseylemt. UNK nit gegleybt.

00:12:36.973 --> 00:12:38.210
hob ikh ir dertseylt

00:12:38.210 --> 00:12:39.189
az ts- e-

00:12:39.189 --> 00:12:42.319
az ikh hob zikh geratevet, az der pape iz mistome shoyn oykh avek

00:12:42.319 --> 00:12:44.209
un di mame iz geshtorbn in geto

00:12:44.209 --> 00:12:46.388
un BERTA mit di kinder hob ikh gelozn.

00:12:46.388 --> 00:12:50.478
ven ikh hob gevolt avekgeyn fun geto, vos ikh hob gehat di bakante fun

00:12:50.676 --> 00:12:51.986
fun Naran

00:12:52.026 --> 00:12:54.182
fleg ikh reydn fun avekgeyn in vald

00:12:54.182 --> 00:12:57.085
flegt mayn tante, mayn mame's a shvester, zogn "a meshugene.

00:12:57.085 --> 00:12:59.785
zikh arayngenumen a mishegas in kop. avekgeyn vinter

00:12:59.785 --> 00:13:04.338
⟨vart khotsh⟩ biz SPRING. avu vestu shlofn, oyfn shney? vest dokh vern farfrorn."

00:13:04.480 --> 00:13:09.047
un ikh hob arayngenumen avekgeyn fun geto, UNK kholem vos der pape hot zikh mir gekholemt.

00:13:09.930 --> 00:13:11.426
iz

00:13:12.681 --> 00:13:13.834
vayz ikh aykh

00:13:13.834 --> 00:13:19.056
az dem tsvelftn MARCH iz shoyn Grodne geven JUDENREIN, un ikh bin avek dem zibetn.

00:13:19.056 --> 00:13:20.437
a monat freyer.

00:13:20.528 --> 00:13:23.596
az zey hobn gehaltn az ikh bin arop fun zinen, zol ikh vartn biz APRIL

00:13:23.596 --> 00:13:25.922
biz s'vet vern varem, s'vet nit zayn keyn shney.

00:13:27.700 --> 00:13:31.035
der iker iz, gey ikh tsu

00:13:31.108 --> 00:13:32.621
tsu LENAn

00:13:32.847 --> 00:13:38.783
un zi hot undz gezogt az zi hot gor nit keyn BARN. zi hot nit afile nit avu tsu farbahaltn, m'hot undz gehatn in shtub.

00:13:38.783 --> 00:13:40.605
a oreme shtub hob ikh gezen.

00:13:40.605 --> 00:13:43.694
un der man hot gehat a ACCIDENT, un er hot a kalike fus

00:13:43.694 --> 00:13:46.706
un er ken gor keyn sakh nit arbetn, epes er arbet ergets

00:13:46.706 --> 00:13:49.496
oyfn RAILROAD epes, un veynik fardint er.

00:13:49.603 --> 00:13:52.904
un, vi es vet vern tog darf ikh avekgeyn.

00:13:53.637 --> 00:13:57.816
un i- ot iz shoyn dinstik. ikh hob ibergeshlofn montik, iz dokh shoyn dinstik.

00:13:57.906 --> 00:14:01.781
dinstik iz BAZARNIY DEN' zogt zi. dinstik iz bay zey a mark tog.

00:14:01.855 --> 00:14:03.826
vel ikh zikh oysmishn mit di goyim

00:14:03.826 --> 00:14:05.673
"un du redst a gutn rusish

00:14:05.673 --> 00:14:08.272
iz geyt ave-" un er zey oykh azoy vi a goyisher yingl

00:14:08.272 --> 00:14:09.682
"iz geyt avek, kinder"

00:14:09.682 --> 00:14:12.172
UNK mir viln dokh kumen avu di

00:14:12.172 --> 00:14:15.377
avu di, UNK, avu yidn lebn dortn

00:14:15.377 --> 00:14:17.306
geratevete fun di shkhite.

00:14:18.038 --> 00:14:20.226
iz gut, hot zi undz gegebn esn

00:14:20.299 --> 00:14:23.476
⟨mir hobn epes opgegesn undz⟩ a shtikl broyt vos zi hot gehat

00:14:23.476 --> 00:14:26.276
vayl eyn mol in tsvey vokhn tsi in dray vokhn bakt zi broyt.

00:14:26.290 --> 00:14:28.868
un, un mir veln aroys fun shtub, un mir geyen

00:14:28.868 --> 00:14:29.945
un mir geyen.

00:14:30.475 --> 00:14:34.552
hobn mir zikh oysgemisht, hert zikh ayn. mir geyen, mir geyen.

00:14:36.195 --> 00:14:37.556
vos iz do geven?

00:14:41.038 --> 00:14:44.570
UNK ⟨hert zikh ayn⟩, azoy vi mir geyen, hobn mir ongegangen oyfn grenets.

00:14:44.570 --> 00:14:46.483
fun vaytn hobn mir gezen a shtabe

00:14:46.759 --> 00:14:48.384
a, a shtabe.

00:14:48.384 --> 00:14:49.541
a shtabe?

00:14:49.541 --> 00:14:51.360
a b- a, a bret.

00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:51.680
oh, yo.

00:14:52.243 --> 00:14:55.231
e- oyf eyn zayt shosey iz a budke, un oyfn ander

00:14:55.231 --> 00:14:57.191
un do shteyt a daytsh, un do iz shoyn der grenets.

00:14:57.191 --> 00:14:58.661
dos endikt zikh shoyn

00:14:58.690 --> 00:15:01.434
driter raykh, un oyfn ander zayt iz OSTLAND.

00:15:01.643 --> 00:15:04.674
hobn mir zikh glaykh gegebn a vorf arayn in rey, in ROW

00:15:04.849 --> 00:15:07.048
hobn zikh arayngevorfn, un mir hobn arayn in vald

00:15:07.048 --> 00:15:08.673
vayl mir UNK mitn ROAD

00:15:08.882 --> 00:15:10.648
hobn mir UNK derzen fun vaytn

00:15:11.025 --> 00:15:12.926
di shtabe. hert zikh ayn.

00:15:14.316 --> 00:15:16.034
WALKen mir, WALKen mir.

00:15:16.034 --> 00:15:17.485
zeen mir fun vaytn

00:15:17.485 --> 00:15:21.279
azoy vi naye, fun di holts, naye, nit keyn gePAINTe hayzer

00:15:21.943 --> 00:15:24.907
⟨epes⟩ ikh veys, efsher UNK a bisl aza

00:15:24.947 --> 00:15:27.641
vi zogt men dos? a SETTLEMENT azoy fun hayzer.

00:15:28.980 --> 00:15:33.243
zog ikh "efsher arayngeyn do betn a shtikl broyt?" mir zaynen shoyn vayter hungerik.

00:15:33.250 --> 00:15:35.117
efsher betn a shtikl broyt do?

00:15:35.308 --> 00:15:38.039
zogt der yingl "neyn, neyn. mir veln nit arayngeyn do.

00:15:38.039 --> 00:15:39.757
kum, mir veln beser geyn vayter."

00:15:40.084 --> 00:15:41.127
kumen mir

00:15:41.127 --> 00:15:44.080
un mir zeen a alte khate, a kleyninke

00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:45.869
efsher ot azoy o vi der tsimer

00:15:45.869 --> 00:15:47.464
a alte holts azelkhe

00:15:47.464 --> 00:15:51.134
di holts azoy fun a sakh regn, fun a sakh UNK shteyt shoyn lange yorn

00:15:51.134 --> 00:15:53.814
dos iz azoy mit grine farvoksn UNK.

00:15:54.647 --> 00:15:56.480
zogt er "kum, mir veln arayngeyn do."

00:15:56.925 --> 00:15:58.336
mir geyen arayn

00:15:58.410 --> 00:15:59.855
a goye

00:16:00.064 --> 00:16:04.057
mit a tikhl oyfn kop farbundn, a oreme khate, oy got.

00:16:04.435 --> 00:16:06.639
gor nit gevust vi poyerim lebn orem.

00:16:07.118 --> 00:16:09.187
hobn mir ir gezogt mir zaynen yidn

00:16:09.295 --> 00:16:11.702
un mir zaynen antlofn fun Grodne. dortn

00:16:11.792 --> 00:16:14.587
nemt men shoyn, reynikt men shoyn oys di letste yidn.

00:16:15.117 --> 00:16:20.089
hot zi gehat a bisl kroyt UNK gevaremt oyf a, a, d- drayfus, oyf aza

00:16:20.196 --> 00:16:22.563
un zi hot undz gegebn im a bisl un mir

00:16:22.563 --> 00:16:25.989
un baym, ikh hob gegangen in volikes, un kh'ho- UNK iz shoyn durkhgegangen taykhlekh.

00:16:25.989 --> 00:16:27.542
kh'veys nit ⟨avu zayn⟩ a brik

00:16:27.542 --> 00:16:29.623
flegn mir bay tog durkhgeyn a taykhl

00:16:29.764 --> 00:16:33.538
iz az mir flegn zikh leygn shlofn fleg geyn a pare fun di fis

00:16:34.303 --> 00:16:35.537
iz zi git undz

00:16:35.537 --> 00:16:38.607
un zi zogt ⟨zi vet⟩ undz tsufirn vayzn avu der grenets

00:16:38.607 --> 00:16:40.557
vayl mir kenen dokh nit geyn mitn ROAD. do iz

00:16:40.557 --> 00:16:44.047
un mir hobn gefregt "vos iz dos far a khates vos mir hobn gezen, azelkhe naye

00:16:44.047 --> 00:16:47.050
naye?" "oy, gut vos ir hot nit arayn." hot zi genumen tseylemen

00:16:47.050 --> 00:16:48.980
"do voynen di POGRANICHNIKES

00:16:48.980 --> 00:16:52.775
di vos, di, di soldatn vos hitn dem bri- dem grenets.

00:16:53.102 --> 00:16:55.731
voynen zey do mit di vayber, mit, mit kinder oykh."

00:16:55.731 --> 00:16:56.710
vi gefelt aykh?

00:16:56.710 --> 00:16:58.462
mir hobn gevolt araynen betn broyt.

00:16:59.751 --> 00:17:00.827
oy, got.

00:17:00.827 --> 00:17:01.941
iz

00:17:01.941 --> 00:17:04.573
zi vet undz tsufirn tsum grenets, undz vayzn avu

00:17:04.573 --> 00:17:07.033
un mir darfn zikh unterleygn, vayle s'iz opgetsoymt

00:17:07.033 --> 00:17:08.438
mit shtekhedike drotn

00:17:08.438 --> 00:17:09.531
un mir darfn zikh

00:17:09.707 --> 00:17:11.323
oy- arunterglitshn.

00:17:11.323 --> 00:17:13.503
veln mir zayn oyfn ander zayt, in OSTLAND.

00:17:14.044 --> 00:17:16.977
hob ikh aroysgenumen fun girtl hundert mark

00:17:16.977 --> 00:17:18.847
a banknot, un ikh hob ir gegebn.

00:17:19.291 --> 00:17:20.871
hot zi dos nit gegleybt.

00:17:20.997 --> 00:17:22.240
un gebetn undz

00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:26.320
az mir veln k- forn, oyb mir veln iberlebn di milkhome ⟨zoln⟩ mir geyn tsurik tsu Gro-

00:17:26.320 --> 00:17:28.350
zoln mir arayngeyn ir z- zen.

00:17:28.350 --> 00:17:30.165
zi vil visn tsi mir hobn ibergelebt.

00:17:30.165 --> 00:17:31.641
oyf tsurik hob ikh nit gehat

00:17:31.641 --> 00:17:33.784
hobn mir geforn. mir hobn gekrogn a RIDE

00:17:33.784 --> 00:17:35.464
fun a rusishn ofitser

00:17:35.464 --> 00:17:37.176
ven d- in fir un fertsiktn yor.

00:17:37.176 --> 00:17:39.530
un er hot zikh nit gevolt opshteln. er hot nit keyn tsayt.

00:17:39.530 --> 00:17:42.040
un aleyn veln mir farlirn dem RIDE. vi veln mir WALKen

00:17:42.040 --> 00:17:43.990
hobn mir gehat gor a sakh tsu geyn.

00:17:43.990 --> 00:17:47.566
hobn mir o- veyst zi nit. meynt zi mistome az me hot undz derharget.

00:17:47.566 --> 00:17:49.286
ikh dertseyl vi dos iz geven.

00:17:50.286 --> 00:17:53.546
hot zi undz tsugefirt. ikh hob zikh geleygt oyfn boykh

00:17:53.546 --> 00:17:55.266
un er, un mir hobn zikh unter

00:17:55.266 --> 00:17:57.270
azoy vi mir zaynen nokhgegangen etlekhe hundert

00:17:57.270 --> 00:17:58.385
meter

00:17:59.117 --> 00:18:03.431
fort a shmoler shlitele, ot azoy shmol vi dos, a UNK

00:18:03.522 --> 00:18:04.809
mit eyn ferd

00:18:04.809 --> 00:18:06.485
un tsvey daytshn zitsn.

00:18:06.846 --> 00:18:08.868
makht eyner "HALT."

00:18:08.868 --> 00:18:10.434
dos meynt blaybt shteyn.

00:18:10.710 --> 00:18:12.707
mir zakhn zikh nit visn. mir geyen

00:18:12.707 --> 00:18:15.157
in vald in, dos iz aza bergl a bisl

00:18:15.157 --> 00:18:16.887
fun dem ROAD, a bisele hekher.

00:18:16.887 --> 00:18:17.825
mir geyen.

00:18:18.102 --> 00:18:21.929
makht er "STOJ" oyf poylish, efsher farshteyen mir nit keyn daytsh

00:18:21.929 --> 00:18:22.941
mir geyen.

00:18:22.941 --> 00:18:25.216
mir hobn UNK ayngetrakht alts eyns iz der sof.

00:18:25.290 --> 00:18:27.562
makht der ander "ACH, LASS SIE GEHEN."

00:18:27.788 --> 00:18:29.582
ken zayn az zey hobn

00:18:29.582 --> 00:18:32.143
aleyn moyre gehat, ver ⟨veys⟩, a poyer ken a-

00:18:30.994 --> 00:18:32.355
zoln zey geyn.

00:18:32.143 --> 00:18:33.213
ye, loz zey geyn.

00:18:33.213 --> 00:18:36.313
, er hot aleyn moyre gehat, hobn zey, tsvey daytshn

00:18:36.313 --> 00:18:39.523
⟨efsher⟩ UNK er ken nemen un shisn UNK dershisn

00:18:39.523 --> 00:18:41.906
un ken zayn take er hot zikh tsugehert tsum gutn.

00:18:42.199 --> 00:18:43.256
me veys nit.

00:18:43.617 --> 00:18:46.389
hobn mir avek. azoy vi mir WALKen, mir WALKen

00:18:46.389 --> 00:18:47.959
dos iz shoyn montik

00:18:47.959 --> 00:18:49.781
emes? neyn, dinstik.

00:18:49.781 --> 00:18:52.385
dinstik. yeder vet zayn nito dinstik.

00:18:53.168 --> 00:18:54.818
zeen mir

00:18:54.818 --> 00:18:56.132
epes a

00:18:56.188 --> 00:18:57.430
a

00:18:57.437 --> 00:18:59.737
likht a sakh in a sht- khate

00:18:59.737 --> 00:19:02.021
zogt er "do kenen mir arayngeyn betn epes.

00:19:02.719 --> 00:19:05.244
efsher mir kenen ibershlofn, betn ⟨der iker⟩

00:19:05.250 --> 00:19:06.830
epes a shtikl broyt."

00:19:07.782 --> 00:19:10.121
faln mir arayn, un do iz a khasene.

00:19:10.633 --> 00:19:12.213
a goyishe khasene.

00:19:12.372 --> 00:19:13.193
oy.

00:19:13.823 --> 00:19:15.707
un me git im glaykh a khap

00:19:16.000 --> 00:19:17.242
un zey reydn

00:19:17.451 --> 00:19:20.651
"kum." un me trogt im branfn. zey zaynen shoyn shiker vi Lot.

00:19:20.758 --> 00:19:22.355
zey faln fun di fis.

00:19:22.648 --> 00:19:23.733
git men im

00:19:23.733 --> 00:19:26.459
hot er gemakht azoy vi er trinkt un hot dos oysgegosn

00:19:26.459 --> 00:19:30.152
nit vern shiker. der yingl hot gehat seykhl, a kluger yingl.

00:19:31.170 --> 00:19:36.429
un, un er makht er visht op di, dem, ⟨dem⟩ lipn fun di branfn.

00:19:36.672 --> 00:19:37.712
un

00:19:37.920 --> 00:19:39.838
un me darf zikh shoyn aroysrukn.

00:19:40.131 --> 00:19:45.941
un mir fregn zikh epes. "avu iz dort?" "UNK." "avu iz d- nokh vayt tsum dorf MEZHANTSY?"

00:19:45.941 --> 00:19:47.637
"oy, iz nokh zeyer vayt.

00:19:47.637 --> 00:19:50.410
oyf vos geyt ir dort?" zog ikh az ikh hob a shvester

00:19:50.410 --> 00:19:52.490
un zi vil mir zoln kumen

00:19:52.490 --> 00:19:54.400
mir, helfn ir ⟨vovn⟩

00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:57.530
